      <div class="container">
        <h2>üåü Why Choose Interactive Whiteboards?</h2>
        <div class="benefits-grid">
          <div class="benefit-card">
            <h3>Boosts Collaboration</h3>
            <p>
              Enhances team engagement through interactive features that allow
              multiple users to contribute simultaneously.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit-card">
            <h3>Ideal for Remote Work</h3>
            <p>
              Perfect for hybrid and remote setups with digital sharing
              capabilities and cloud integration.
            </p>
