              <li class="pro">‚úÖ Scalable, cost-effective</li>
              <li class="con">
                ‚ùå Sensitive to external conditions (sunlight/dust)
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="touch-tech-card">
            <h3>Electromagnetic (EMR)</h3>
            <ul class="pros-cons">
              <li class="pro">‚úÖ Extremely precise, pressure-sensitive</li>
              <li class="con">‚ùå Requires special pen; expensive</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="touch-tech-card">
            <h3>Capacitive</h3>
            <ul class="pros-cons">
              <li class="pro">‚úÖ Highly responsive; sleek</li>
              <li class="con">‚ùå Not compatible with gloves; higher cost</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="touch-tech-card">
            <h3>Optical Imaging</h3>
            <ul class="pros-cons">
              <li class="pro">‚úÖ Easy to install, scalable</li>
              <li class="con">‚ùå Accuracy impacted by lighting/shadows</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="touch-tech-card">
            <h3>Resistive (Legacy)</h3>
            <ul class="pros-cons">
              <li class="pro">‚úÖ Low cost, versatile input</li>
              <li class="con">‚ùå Poor clarity and durability; outdated</li>
            </ul>
