            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        <div class="cta-container">
          <a href="#" class="button-ghost"
            >Download the Full Comparison Table [PDF] ‚Üí</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="combinations" class="content-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>üí∞ Best Combinations by Use Case & Budget</h2>
        <div class="combinations-grid">
          <div class="combination-card">
            <h3>Education (Budget-Friendly)</h3>
            <p><strong>Recommended:</strong> LED Display + IR Touch</p>
            <p>
              Balances affordability with durability for classroom environments.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="combination-card">
            <h3>Creative Industries (High Precision)</h3>
            <p><strong>Recommended:</strong> OLED Display + EMR Touch</p>
            <p>
              Provides exceptional color accuracy and pen precision for detailed
